2.0.0
https://github.com/CodyTolene/pip-boy-3000-holotapes/pull/53
- Turn iPip into a full media player with music, video, and image support.
- Add a menu (MUSIC, VIDEOS, IMAGES).
- Move the music player to its own screen.
- Add a video player.
- Add an image viewer.
- Create the "VIDEOS" and "IMAGES" folders automatically on launch if missing.

1.2.1
https://github.com/CodyTolene/pip-boy-3000-holotapes/pull/27
